Reading the support material for this I believe the normative and informative
description of the structure of the block of bytes returned by the get machine
description API should be in the API spec, and have asked Ash to move it there.

The rest of the document - describing nodes and the properties within
them - seems akin to a bus binding.

The first machine description case will help to set the expectation
for the layout of such cases.

When we have a document ready, opinions on my viewpoint will
be good.

Tony.



